Package: sar
Type: Package
Title: Convenience Access to 'Sysstat', 'SAR', 'SADF' Data as Data.Frames, JSON, XML
Description: Making available system statistics systems with commandline tool 
    'sar' and 'sadf' (a standard tool to collect system statistics on Unix 
    like systems). The pacakge does provide the data collected by 'sar' and 
    friends as an easily accessible and processable data.frame, JSON string, 
    or XML string. Using the systems SSH client its possible to collect data 
    from remote servers and return access in the local session. 
